Usage: reportLengthViolation [-help] [-excNetFile <fileName>] [-histogram]
                             [-outfile <fileName>] [-selNetFile <fileName>]
                             [-significant_digits <integer>] [-all  | -noGlobalNets ]

-help                             # Prints out the command usage
-all                              # Report all option  (bool, optional)
-excNetFile <fileName>            # List of Nets not to report 
                                  # (string, optional)
-histogram                        # Print a histogram  (bool, optional)
-noGlobalNets                     # NO global net option  (bool, optional)
-outfile <fileName>               # Output file name  (string, optional)
-selNetFile <fileName>            # List of nets to report  (string, optional)
-significant_digits <integer>     # Number of significant digits option 
                                  # (int, optional)